ZH: 这条路上到处都是坑洼。
EN: The road is full of potholes.

ZH: 下雨之后，院子里的地面都变得坑洼不平了。
EN: After the rain, the ground in the yard became uneven with potholes.

ZH: 要小心骑车，不要被坑洼绊倒了。
EN: Be careful when riding a bike, don't get tripped up by the potholes.

ZH: 这个地方常年积水，形成了很多坑洼。
EN: This place has standing water all year round, forming many potholes.

ZH: 街道上的坑洼给驾驶者带来了不便。
EN: The potholes on the street inconvenience drivers.

ZH: 我绊到坑洼摔倒了。
EN: I tripped over a pothole and fell down.

ZH: 让我们把这些坑洼填平，让地面平坦起来。
EN: Let's fill in these potholes and level the ground.

ZH: 坑洼的路面增加了行车的难度。
EN: The bumpy road with potholes makes driving more difficult.

ZH: 这个停车场到处是坑洼，应该重新修整一下。
EN: The parking lot is full of potholes and needs to be repaired.

ZH: 大雨后，道路上出现了许多坑洼。
EN: After heavy rain, many potholes appeared on the road.

ZH: 骑自行车的时候一定要小心坑洼的地面。
EN: Be careful of the potholed ground when riding a bike.

ZH: 她不小心踩进了一个深深的坑洼里。
EN: She accidentally stepped into a deep pothole.

ZH: 这些坑洼容易导致车辆损坏。
EN: These potholes can easily cause damage to vehicles.

ZH: 请小心绕过路上的坑洼。
EN: Please be careful to avoid the potholes on the road.

ZH: 路上的坑洼使得行人不敢贸然通过。
EN: The potholes on the road make pedestrians hesitant to cross.

ZH: 这个公园的草坪上布满了坑洼。
EN: The lawn in this park is full of potholes.

ZH: 天天经过这些坑洼的路段，车辆很容易产生故障。
EN: Vehicles are prone to breakdowns when passing through these potholed sections every day.

ZH: 请你们解决路面上的坑洼问题。
EN: Please solve the problem of potholes on the road.

ZH: 去年修好的道路现在又出现了一些新的坑洼。
EN: Some new potholes have appeared on the road that was repaired last year.

ZH: 行走时要注意脚下，以免掉进坑洼里。
EN: Be careful where you step to avoid falling into potholes.
